title: Steelers-Browns, Myles Garrett, Baker Mayfield, & the Blazing 5
itunes:title: Steelers-Browns, Myles Garrett, Baker Mayfield, & the Blazing 5
description:
Colin discusses the violent end of the Steelers-Browns Thursday night game, Myles Garrett's suspension, Baker Mayfield's response, and his new Blazing 5 picks for the weekend. Guests include Danny Kanell, Eric Dickerson, DeForest Buckner, Jason McIntyre, and T. J. Houshmandzadeh.
